{"tid":2445132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"打鼓嶺警車私家車相撞 5人受傷送院包括4警員","createTime":"2021-03-13T11:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T11:54:52.000Z","uid":295224,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2a18d8b10178a7b48e522c9d0ba76e70615e88","tid":2445132,"uid":295224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"打鼓嶺坪輋路中午發生交通意外，一輛私家車與一輛警車相撞。事件中共有5人受傷，包括4名警員。<br />\n<br />\n事發在中午12時23分，一輛警車沿坪輋路往沙頭角公路方向行駛，當駛至打鼓嶺坪輋路時，一輛私家車從一停車場駛出至坪輋路，兩車其後相撞。事發後，警車及私家車的車頭位置均有損毀。在涉事警車上，負責駕駛的男警務人員腰部受傷，車上另外3名男警務人員輕傷，至於39歲李姓私家車司機則腿部受傷。受傷的5人清醒，被送往北區醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A%E8%88%87-tesla-%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-2-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%2588%2587-tesla-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E-2-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=2553d35b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%2588%2587-tesla-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E-2-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%2F&h=2595514e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A%E8%88%87-tesla-%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-2-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"a8a7493b1263e89867b18ebea87e425862bcecaa","tid":2445132,"uid":268519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"2021/2/15"},{"pid":"5b942099030499bc71